### PN Variant Comparison (200 runs each)

| Variant | CEP50 (m) | Pk (%) | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| PPN (N=3) | 2644 | 0.0 | Altitude channel broken — no vertical guidance |
| TPN (N=5) | 340 | 1.0 | Primary variant, full altitude tracking |
